name: Gustavosta/Stable-Diffusion-Prompts
description: The Stable Diffusion Dataset, created by Gustavosta, is a comprehensive collection of 80,000 image prompts sourced from the Lexica.art image finder. The dataset was compiled despite the challenges of working with a search engine that does not have a public API without Cloudflare protection. To test the dataset, visit spaces/Gustavosta/MagicPrompt-Stable-Diffusion, and to view the model, go to Gustavosta/MagicPrompt-Stable-Diffusion. This dataset is an essential resource for researchers and developers working with the Stable Diffusion model for image generation.
